OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA wet start with outbreaks of
OL,6,Frain, heaviest and most persistent
OL,7,Fover the Welsh hills. Somewhat drier
OL,8,Finto the afternoon through still
OL,9,Fdrizzle in places. Windy, particularly
OL,10,Flater around coasts.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA windy evening with a risk
OL,13,Fof coastal gales. Often cloudy with
OL,14,Ffurther spells of rain moving into the
OL,15,Fwest during the early morning. Lighter
OL,16,Fwinds by dawn. Mild.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
