OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FUnsettled to begin the new
OL,6,Fweek as rain sweeps eastwards across
OL,7,FWales, heavy at times over hills.
OL,8,FWinds easing through the day.
OL,9,FRemaining mild for the time of year.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FCloudy
OL,12,Fon Tuesday with some patchy rain,
OL,13,Fbefore turning drier and brighter on
OL,14,FWednesday. Dry on Thursday with some
OL,15,Ffurther rain possible later. Feeling
OL,16,Fpleasant in any sunny spells.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
